Project Manager 

The system that our team is creating is a lookup system for books using a website. It will be free to all users, and the way it works is the user will input a book
or keyword they want to find, and from there it will add in the book name and how much it costs. The system will use the website that the user will input, using a 
part of the book's name that the user will input. It will tell the user the full name of the book, along with the pricing of the book, and if it successfully 
pulled up the book. If the system couldn’t pull up the book, it would give the user an error message, and the user would have the option to re-enter the 
information that gave them the error.

What the Program Needs
Website link to scrape

Input system for a book or a keyword in a book

Add the book name and how much it would cost.

Keyword or title of book

Full name of book and price

Error message if the code breaks
